This paper deals with the abuse of web push notifications for advertising purposes, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also involves data collection and analysis, which could fall under information retrieval (cs.IR) and social and information networks (cs.SI). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of ad-blocking software and browser extensions, which could fall under multimedia (cs.MM) and networking and internet architecture (cs.NI).
